text: "You Can Do It" is a single by Ice Cube. You Can Do It may also refer to: * "You can do it!", a catchphrase used by actor Rob Schneider * "You Can Do It" (No Doubt song) * "You can do it", a catchphrase by fitness and weight loss specialist Tony Little ==See also== * We Can Do It (disambiguation) * You Can Do That * You Do It
